main event: A UFO report from Camp Holabird, Maryland on October 3, 1949.
interesting points: The report mentions a photograph showing an outdoor scene but lacks any discernible UFOs., The time of the photograph is noted as 0930 hours., The camera used was a Speed Graphic with Super XX film., The photograph was taken with a setting of 1/100, F 11, Infinity., One visible sign in the photograph appears to say 'ENTRANCE'.
